Make it so other people can see it? What do you mean by that statement?

New codes for JDK
[b]

CLASSPATH VARIABLE[/b]

CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_26\bin;%CLASSPATH%;C:\Program Files\Java\jre6\lib\ext\QTJava.zip

If you have windows 7, you could have Program Files(x86) instead.

PATH VARIABLE

[quote]
C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_26\bin;[/quote]

A working compiler…

[quote]@echo off
Title Compiling…
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_26\bin\javac.exe” *.java
pause [/quote]

Hope that helps.[/quote]
